casebody.data:
Heintz, Respondent, v. Everard, Appellant. Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 14, 1892.) Action by Jacob Heintz against James Everard.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

D. M. Newberger, for appellant. H. & K. Forster, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed.
